OL,6,FGranada Reports political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Elaine Willcox was at
OL,8,Fthe protest in London.
OL,10,FA family are calling on the government
OL,11,Fto take responsibility after claiming
OL,12,Fdebt caused by defective wall cavity
OL,13,Finsulation contributed to their
OL,14,Ffather's death.
OL,16,FIan Lofthouse died on 1 May 2024 after
OL,17,Fhe was admitted to hospital with
OL,18,Fpneumonia, later developing
OL,19,Fencephalitis and kidney failure and
OL,20,Fthen suffering a stroke.
