OL,3,CDebt caused by cavity wall scandal
OL,4,C'contributed to dad's death'
OL,6,FThe 74-year-old was one of many who
OL,7,Fused government backed grants to have
OL,8,Fcavity wall insulation installed in
OL,9,Ftheir property, but often that work
OL,10,Fwas defective and caused damp and
OL,11,Fmould.
OL,13,FMr Lofthouse was in debt after SSB
OL,14,FLaw, a Sheffield-based law firm, went
OL,15,Finto liquidation after promising
OL,16,Fhundreds of people they could sue to
OL,17,Fpay for repairs on a no win, no fee
OL,18,Fbasis.
