OL,6,FThe legal fees were then passed on to
OL,7,Fhomeowner, leaving them with
OL,8,Fsignificant debt and serious issues
OL,9,Fwith their homes.
OL,11,FMr Lofthouse's son, Christian
OL,12,FLofthouse, and his sister, Rebecca,
OL,13,Fwere among protesters who gathered
OL,14,Foutside parliament to plead for
OL,15,Fgovernment support.
OL,17,F"18 months ago, he was still dancing
OL,18,Fthe night away on the northern soul
OL,19,Fscene. He would go out on weekenders,
OL,20,Fhe used to go to Amsterdam with his
OL,21,Ffriends," said Christian.
