OL,6,F"With this whole situation, the damp
OL,7,Faffected his physical health, he had
OL,8,FChronic obstructive pulmonary disease
OL,9,F(COPD) and also had asthma, living in
OL,10,Fa house with that, with those health
OL,11,Fconditions, his health deteriorated so
OL,12,Fquickly.
OL,14,F"There was also the mental effect,
OL,15,Fwith SSB law. They came round, said we
OL,16,Fhad a good case and they could get the
OL,17,Fhouses fixed and get compensation.
OL,19,F"The company then went into
OL,20,Fliquidation."
