OL,6,F"I believe the government has got some
OL,7,Fresponsibility, for giving contracts
OL,8,Fto people who obviously weren't fit to
OL,9,Fdo the job and secondly, the law firms
OL,10,Fwho promised a no win no fee are now
OL,11,Fputting charges on people's home.
OL,13,F"These are people that cannot afford
OL,14,Fit, they're trapped, they cannot sell
OL,15,Ftheir house, they cannot afford the
OL,16,Fbill."
OL,18,FLike many others, the Lofthouse family
OL,19,Fsay they had no issues with damp or
OL,20,Fcondensation prior to the government
OL,21,Fscheme.
