OL,6,FChristian added: "They were told it
OL,7,Fwas a government backed scheme, It
OL,8,Fwould help with the insulation and the
OL,9,Fheating bills in the winter. They
OL,10,Fthought it's a government backed
OL,11,Fscheme...it's been approved by them,
OL,12,Fwe'll do it.
OL,14,F"(My Mum) she's on a state pension,
OL,15,Fthere's nothing she can do about it
OL,16,Fand now she's lost her husband...it
OL,17,Fwould have been their 52nd wedding
OL,18,Fanniversary next month.
